query.sparql: select ?uri where { res:Airline dbo:programme dbr:Frequent flyer }
select count ( distinct ?num ) where { res:University_of_Amsterdam dbo:class ?num }
select distinct ?uri where { res:Garry_Green_ ( actor ) dbo:ethnicity ?uri }
select distinct ?uri where { dbr:Soccer_in_Paris dbo:influenced ?uri . ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person ; dbo:influenced ?uri } order by desc ( ?uri ) offset 0 limit 1
select distinct ?date where { dbr:Muhammad_Abdel_Saud ( persian ) dbp:deathDate ?date }
select ?uri where { res:The_Pillars_of_the_Earth dbo:numberOfPages ?x . ?x dbo:author ?uri } order by desc ( count ( ?uri ) ) offset 0 limit 1
